.
</p><p>The only known cycle is <span class=3D"texhtml">(1,2)</span> of peri=
od 2, called the trivial cycle.
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Cycle_length">Cycle length<=
/h3></div>
<p>As of 2025, the best known bound on cycle length is <span class=3D"nowra=
p"><span data-sort-value=3D"7011217976794617000=E2=99=A0"></span>217<span s=
