55<span style=3D"margin-left:.25em;">504</span><span style=3D"margin-left:.=
25em;">839</span><span style=3D"margin-left:.25em;">929</span></span> witho=
ut shortcut).<sup id=3D"cite_ref-Barina_13-1" class=3D"reference"><a href=
=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Collatz_conjecture#cite_note-Barina-13"><=
span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>12<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span>=
</a></sup> In 1993, Eliahou proved that the period <span class=3D"texhtml m=
var" style=3D"font-style:italic;">p</span> of any non-trivial cycle is of t=
he form
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
