</p><p>Hailstone sequences can be computed by the <a href=3D"https://en.wik=
ipedia.org/wiki/Tag_system#Example:_Computation_of_Collatz_sequences" title=
=3D"Tag system">2-tag system</a> with production rules
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"texhtml"><i>a</i> =E2=86=92 <i>bc</i></span>, <span =
class=3D"texhtml"><i>b</i> =E2=86=92 <i>a</i></span>, <span class=3D"texhtm=
